title: Full Show (Bucs and Packers both lose, Cowboys defeat Lions in Dak's return, Lakers and Russell Westbrook)
description:
00:00 Bucs fall to Panthers 21-3
25:16 Cowboys beat Lions 24-6 in Dak's return from injury
56:44 Who's most responsible for team falling under .500, Brady or Rodgers?
1:11:56 With Dak back, does Dallas once again have the best QB in the NFC East?
1:23:07 Should Darvin Ham move Russ back to the bench
1:35:03 Surprised Tom Brady is below .500 through 7 games for first time since 2002?
1:44:17 Patrick Mahomes: 423 pass yds, 3 TD in win over 49ers
1:48:44 Cowboys force 5 turnovers in 24-6 win over the Lions
1:55:14 Referee appears to ask for Mike Evans' autograph after Bucs loss
